es/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8a6586a5e3ae765825a6eb1a8b3a6458e15013","tid":573953,"uid":56311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca0d8b50197cfc0337f22e543cf4b01444fccf85","tid":573953,"uid":48083,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:32:54.000Z","msg":"屈穎妍大變臉 《壹》仔筆神變親共藍絲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從前有一個記者雄心壯志，1995年以旅遊為名潛入福建，可惜佢唔小心俾人揭發咗，話佢非法搜集中國軍事機密，最後被驅逐出境。佢當時喺傳媒界都十分出名，仲有筆神之稱。估唔估到佢係邊個呢？佢就係出哂名愛國愛港又撐警嘅專欄作家屈穎妍喇。二十年前，佢其實係《壹》仔嘅一分子嚟㗎。 <br />\n<br />\n屈穎妍近年政治立場一百八十度大轉變，唔單止幫689寫本叫《這個特首不太冷》嘅書，更長期發表備受爭議嘅言論，例如雨傘運動期間七警暗角打鑊事件，佢認為「警員要面對長期的情緒壓抑，爆發是遲早的事」，之後仲表示「是因為不想教，更因為不懂教」，辭去浸大新聞系兼職講師一職。 <br />\n<br />\n佢嘅出位言論唔只咁少：一三年寫「除了粗口，我們真的沒東西值得拍掌歡呼嗎？」，但係出席撐警集會聽到阿sir爆粗就拍就拍爛手掌；前年，警方拉錯一名智障自閉男子，指控佢涉嫌誤殺，屈穎妍又為阿Sir護航，大讚警方表現係完美保障受害人；話恥與明報為伍，罷寫專欄；林慧思事件；廢青芭蕉扇事件；撐七警言論，指責曾健超一個人渣毀咗七段人生&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n有曾經同佢共事過嘅《壹》仔同事話，當年十分尊敬呢個前輩，對佢呢幾年突然變面都深感困惑，仲話好失望添。 <br />\n<br />\n撰文：巫不言 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20170714/2_528504_0/%E5%B1%88%E7%A9%8E%E5%A6%8D%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%8A%E8%87%89-%E5%A3%B9-%E4%BB%94%E7%AD%86%E7%A5%9E%E8%AE%8A%E8%A6%AA%E5%85%B1%E8%97%8D%E7%B5%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20170714%2F2_528504_0%2F%25E5%25B1%2588%25E7%25A9%258E%25E5%25A6%258D%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25AE%258A%25E8%2587%2589-%25E5%25A3%25B9-%25E4%25BB%2594%25E7%25AD%2586%25E7%25A5%259E%25E8%25AE%258A%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%2585%25B1%25E8%2597%258D%25E7%25B5%25B2&d=u9aNrW9w0vJ2xZCPsOckSSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=606c4718\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20170714%2F2_528504_0%2F%25E5%25B1%2588%25E7%25A9%258E%25E5%25A6%258D%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25AE%258A%25E8%2587%2589-%25E5%25A3%25B9-%25E4%25BB%2594%25E7%25AD%2586%25E7%25A5%259E%25E8%25AE%258A%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%2585%25B1%25E8%2597%258D%25E7%25B5%25B2&h=6b483f72\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20170714/2_528504_0/%E5%B1%88%E7%A9%8E%E5%A6%8D%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%8A%E8%87%89-%E5%A3%B9-%E4%BB%94%E7%AD%86%E7%A5%9E%E8%AE%8A%E8%A6%AA%E5%85%B1%E8%97%8D%E7%B5%B2</a><br />\n<br />\n佢老公都好似冇再點屌政府<br />\n有冇人知佢兩個有咩痛腳俾中共揸住?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T06:01:40.000Z","msg":"揸咩撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n揾食之嘛,典型香港人格"},{"pid":"339c4695845842869e62ffd8fb3623253daba205","tid":573953,"uid":160414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T06:02:24.000Z","msg":"要不是佔中 佢都無得廢噏咁耐呃飯食"},{"pid":"e93ed9ac696bffd57d846483fc1274b955ee89e2","tid":573953,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T06:05:42.000Z","msg":"佔中已成百搭籍口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee907766f5fd3f42bf543748b29f9f466e8a5b96","tid":573953,"uid":83212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T06:07:06.000Z","msg":"屈穎妍真係姓屈架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無改錯姓"},{"pid":"29af509dc450031c232ba2ddf8ca68d84c5dbfb6","tid":573953,"uid":23180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T06:08:12.000Z","msg":"幾時攞孔子科學獎<br />\n<br />\n條癲婆已經搵倒呢樣野去解釋宇宙萬物所有野"},{"pid":"e366f7e60bea25c65c8ae1778250e61717ae3455","tid":573953,"uid":25179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T06:09:09.000Z","msg":"佢真係痴撚左線"},{"pid":"071dc0485e6e007b665ec255c329ebabb8331287","tid":573953,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T06:09:20.000Z","msg":"最搞笑係，佢啲女係响英國讀書，外國勢力，你懂的!"},{"pid":"23d4f86c8bf46a8122ccd03cc943d674fba6acb1","tid":573953,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T06:19:18.000Z","msg":"佔中夠佢講一世"},{"pid":"7bc5faf95b5712c7ef8620e5b223f23b421603fa","tid":573953,"uid":43173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-2